data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!!! MOTIVATED SELLER!!!  Come check out this BEAUTIFUL POOL home in South Oak Village located in Sugarmill Woods! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom split floor plan home offers a master bedroom with a large bathroom, 2 walk-in closets and sliding glass doors to screened in lanai. When you walk in the front door you will enter into the living room that also has sliding glass doors to the screened in lanai with a refreshing pool where you can plan your next BBQ!!! New roof in 2021, Pool is heated with new tiles and new ladder. Schedule your showing today!!!
